1
00:01:33,320 --> 00:01:34,040
Please stay.

2
00:01:34,400 --> 00:01:36,000
It's what Xingxing and I truly feel.

3
00:01:36,440 --> 00:01:37,440
No matter where you are,

4
00:01:37,880 --> 00:01:39,480
you can realize your true value.

5
00:01:43,760 --> 00:01:44,880
No, I...

6
00:01:47,080 --> 00:01:48,480
I... I signed up for a tour group.

7
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:50,800
It's okay.

8
00:01:51,080 --> 00:01:52,320
When Xingxing's on vacation,

9
00:01:52,400 --> 00:01:53,320
the three of us

10
00:01:53,400 --> 00:01:56,400
will book a super-duper luxury tour.

11
00:01:56,400 --> 00:01:57,080
Okay, Xingxing?

12
00:01:57,080 --> 00:01:57,800
Yes, yes.

13
00:01:57,800 --> 00:01:59,120
The three of us will travel together then.

14
00:01:59,440 --> 00:02:00,240
It's settled.

15
00:02:00,240 --> 00:02:00,720
Okay.

16
00:02:00,720 --> 00:02:01,240
Xiao Min.

17
00:02:01,240 --> 00:02:01,880
Let's go.

18
00:02:01,880 --> 00:02:02,520
Xiao Min,

19
00:02:02,520 --> 00:02:04,120
take your Mama Xin Ran home.

20
00:02:04,240 --> 00:02:05,120
Let's go.

21
00:02:05,280 --> 00:02:06,360
What are you doing?

22
00:02:06,480 --> 00:02:08,840
Lin Yiran, the appeal verdict is in.

23
00:02:08,919 --> 00:02:10,280
We won!

24
00:02:23,240 --> 00:02:24,240
A bit deeper.

25
00:02:26,320 --> 00:02:26,560
That's it.

26
00:02:26,560 --> 00:02:27,280
Look.

27
00:02:27,320 --> 00:02:28,320
Come, take a look.

28
00:02:28,320 --> 00:02:28,920
Good.

29
00:02:29,080 --> 00:02:29,840
Here, place it here.

30
00:02:30,720 --> 00:02:31,480
Yes, take that...

31
00:02:31,480 --> 00:02:33,040
Support the bottom with your left hand.

32
00:02:33,360 --> 00:02:34,560
Yes, that's right.

33
00:02:34,560 --> 00:02:35,560
Now, slowly.

34
00:02:35,680 --> 00:02:36,320
Slowly now.

35
00:02:36,520 --> 00:02:37,280
Press it tight.

36
00:02:38,040 --> 00:02:38,800
Press tight.

37
00:02:40,120 --> 00:02:40,760
One,

38
00:02:41,120 --> 00:02:41,760
two,

39
00:02:41,960 --> 00:02:42,480
three,

40
00:02:42,560 --> 00:02:43,160
lift!

41
00:02:45,120 --> 00:02:45,640
Amazing!

42
00:02:47,680 --> 00:02:49,040
Stop messing around.

43
00:02:55,600 --> 00:02:57,200
One, two, three.

44
00:02:57,200 --> 00:02:58,000
Cheese!

45
00:02:58,000 --> 00:02:59,120
One, two, three, cheese!

46
00:02:59,120 --> 00:02:59,920
Smile!

47
00:04:06,360 --> 00:04:07,400
Brother Taibai

48
00:04:07,720 --> 00:04:09,040
Brother Taibai

49
00:04:09,320 --> 00:04:10,720
Banished Immortal, do not hurry

50
00:04:11,080 --> 00:04:12,320
Wang Lun has come

51
00:04:14,760 --> 00:04:15,840
I've come to see you off

52
00:04:16,959 --> 00:04:19,959
This journey spans mountains and rivers

53
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:24,760
Sadly, I cannot travel alongside you

54
00:04:25,360 --> 00:04:28,320
Who knows when we shall meet again

55
00:04:29,040 --> 00:04:32,120
Though I lack your literary gift

56
00:04:33,440 --> 00:04:39,480
please take this Xuan paper I formed myself

57
00:04:40,440 --> 00:04:42,080
to carry the grand ambition

58
00:04:42,640 --> 00:04:46,600
of boundless rivers and mountains we both hold dear

59
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:49,920
Thank you for your kindness, brother

60
00:04:59,360 --> 00:05:00,440
Someday in the future

61
00:05:01,120 --> 00:05:04,360
should I return to Xuanzhou

62
00:05:05,280 --> 00:05:10,200
I shall admire the endless peach blossoms with you

63
00:05:11,280 --> 00:05:14,720
and share the finest wines of every household

64
00:05:16,400 --> 00:05:17,200
Excellent

65
00:05:19,480 --> 00:05:20,600
Rest assured, brother

66
00:05:22,880 --> 00:05:24,520
The waters of Peach Blossom Pond

67
00:05:25,360 --> 00:05:28,600
will remember your song for me

68
00:05:29,880 --> 00:05:35,120
These green hills and waters will remember

69
00:05:39,760 --> 00:05:41,120
your friendship for me

70
00:05:42,880 --> 00:05:43,720
Brother Taibai

71
00:05:45,720 --> 00:05:46,520
Take care

72
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:49,800
Take care

73
00:05:57,040 --> 00:06:00,760
Aboard my boat, I, Li Bai, was set to go.

74
00:06:01,320 --> 00:06:05,200
When suddenly on shore your farewell songs o'erflow.

75
00:06:05,640 --> 00:06:09,400
The Peach Blossom Pool is a thousand feet deep

76
00:06:09,840 --> 00:06:13,760
Not as deep as your love for me

77
00:06:14,240 --> 00:06:18,400
Aboard my boat, I, Li Bai, was set to go.

78
00:06:18,520 --> 00:06:22,320
When suddenly on shore your farewell songs o'erflow.

79
00:06:22,720 --> 00:06:26,760
The Peach Blossom Pool is a thousand feet deep

80
00:06:26,840 --> 00:06:31,280
Not as deep as your love for me

81
00:06:32,480 --> 00:06:34,400
The Peach Blossom Pool is a thousand feet deep

82
00:06:34,640 --> 00:06:36,760
Not as deep as your love for me

83
00:06:37,120 --> 00:06:39,040
Li Bai left behind more than just poetry

84
00:06:39,400 --> 00:06:41,400
He also left the hospitality of Peach Blossom Town's

85
00:06:41,400 --> 00:06:43,320
Xuan paper artisans, passed down for generations

86
00:06:43,640 --> 00:06:44,400
Friendship

87
00:06:45,120 --> 00:06:46,320
Speaking of friendship

88
00:06:46,640 --> 00:06:50,040
For the future and growth of Peach Blossom Town's Xuan paper

89
00:06:50,760 --> 00:06:54,400
Ms. Xin Ran is willing to stand together

90
00:06:54,400 --> 00:06:55,720
with the Xuan paper artisans of Peach Blossom Town

91
00:06:55,840 --> 00:06:57,120
And she will take the position of

92
00:06:57,160 --> 00:07:00,520
General Manager of the Xuan Paper Cultural and Creative Cooperative

93
00:07:19,520 --> 00:07:20,440
Thank you, President Xiao.

94
00:07:29,960 --> 00:07:31,840
Let me first thank everyone here.

95
00:07:34,600 --> 00:07:37,080
Thanks to the Peach Blossom Town government,

96
00:07:37,520 --> 00:07:41,160
and to all my colleagues in the Xuan Paper Association.

97
00:07:42,280 --> 00:07:43,040
Please, please.

98
00:07:43,040 --> 00:07:43,960
No need to be so formal.

99
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:45,440
It's our pleasure, truly.

100
00:07:47,200 --> 00:07:47,760
I...

101
00:07:49,480 --> 00:07:51,320
This appointment letter in my hand,

102
00:07:52,040 --> 00:07:52,960
honestly speaking,

103
00:07:53,400 --> 00:07:54,840
carries extraordinary meaning.

104
00:07:55,520 --> 00:07:58,080
Back then, Li Bai and Wang Lun

105
00:07:58,080 --> 00:08:00,440
created a beautiful tale right here.

106
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:03,240
Today, through Xuan paper cultural and creative work,

107
00:08:03,240 --> 00:08:04,720
we join hands together.

108
00:08:05,200 --> 00:08:06,200
I believe

109
00:08:06,640 --> 00:08:09,040
we can all work together

110
00:08:09,240 --> 00:08:12,160
to write a legend of a new era.

111
00:08:12,840 --> 00:08:14,280
Our great ship of Xuan paper creativity

112
00:08:14,280 --> 00:08:16,160
has officially set sail.

113
00:08:16,600 --> 00:08:18,840
I'm willing to work alongside everyone

114
00:08:19,080 --> 00:08:20,240
to create a brilliant future together.

115
00:08:20,240 --> 00:08:21,720
Thank you all once again.

116
00:08:50,200 --> 00:08:52,920
Muyantang Cultural Creative Store is now open!

117
00:08:53,240 --> 00:08:54,480
Welcome, welcome, welcome!

118
00:08:54,480 --> 00:08:54,880
Come on in!

119
00:08:54,880 --> 00:08:55,640
Thank you, thank you, thank you.

120
00:08:55,640 --> 00:08:58,160
Congratulations, congratulations!

121
00:08:58,160 --> 00:08:59,960
Thank you, thank you.

122
00:08:59,960 --> 00:09:01,200
Thanks for coming out to support us!

123
00:09:01,200 --> 00:09:01,960
Thank you, thank you.

124
00:09:01,960 --> 00:09:02,480
Welcome, welcome, welcome!

125
00:09:02,480 --> 00:09:03,680
Congratulations, congratulations!

126
00:09:04,400 --> 00:09:05,160
Best wishes on your grand opening!

127
00:09:05,160 --> 00:09:05,880
You made it, you made it.

128
00:09:05,880 --> 00:09:06,640
Congratulations!

129
00:09:06,640 --> 00:09:07,480
Great, great, great.

130
00:09:07,480 --> 00:09:08,440
Congratulations, congratulations!

131
00:09:08,440 --> 00:09:09,720
The very first store, the first one!

132
00:09:09,720 --> 00:09:10,160
Thank you, thank you.

133
00:09:10,160 --> 00:09:10,840
Congratulations!

134
00:09:10,840 --> 00:09:12,440
The pride of Peach Blossom Town!

135
00:09:12,440 --> 00:09:13,160
Congratulations!

136
00:09:14,080 --> 00:09:14,600
Come on!

137
00:09:14,880 --> 00:09:15,720
Please give us your guidance.

138
00:09:15,720 --> 00:09:17,920
Thank you, thank you.

139
00:09:18,320 --> 00:09:18,840
Come, come, come.

140
00:09:18,840 --> 00:09:20,400
Right this way. Thank you so much.

141
00:09:20,440 --> 00:09:23,960
Ahead lies a bright new future.

142
00:09:24,280 --> 00:09:28,240
Behind us, a thousand years of wisdom.

143
00:09:28,640 --> 00:09:29,920
Tradition and innovation:

144
00:09:30,240 --> 00:09:33,080
seemingly opposed, yet truly symbiotic.

145
00:09:33,400 --> 00:09:35,480
Tradition is the foundation of civilization,

146
00:09:35,680 --> 00:09:36,680
a river formed by countless ancestors

147
00:09:36,680 --> 00:09:39,720
pooling together their experience.

148
00:09:40,040 --> 00:09:40,960
And what about innovation?

149
00:09:41,760 --> 00:09:44,840
It's breaking through the entrenched dams,

150
00:09:44,840 --> 00:09:45,840
giving this river

151
00:09:45,840 --> 00:09:48,640
new directions and new possibilities.

152
00:09:48,760 --> 00:09:51,160
This is what I want to share with you today:

153
00:09:51,320 --> 00:09:55,200
the mission of the new Xuan paper artisan.

154
00:09:55,560 --> 00:09:56,440
In my view,

155
00:09:57,200 --> 00:10:00,480
tradition is not the shackle of innovation.

156
00:10:01,280 --> 00:10:02,760
It's the springboard for innovation.

157
00:10:02,960 --> 00:10:03,720
And innovation

158
00:10:04,200 --> 00:10:06,360
is never a betrayal of tradition,

159
00:10:06,480 --> 00:10:08,520
but rather its continuation.

160
00:10:08,760 --> 00:10:10,560
We honor the older generation of Xuan paper artisans,

161
00:10:10,560 --> 00:10:13,000
but we'll never cling blindly to the old ways.

162
00:10:13,000 --> 00:10:14,520
We embrace the changes in the market,

163
00:10:14,520 --> 00:10:15,920
but we'll never blindly

164
00:10:16,480 --> 00:10:18,560
follow the crowd, either.

165
00:10:18,760 --> 00:10:20,480
We want to root innovation

166
00:10:20,680 --> 00:10:22,840
deep in the soil of tradition,

167
00:10:23,160 --> 00:10:26,120
so it can stand firm

168
00:10:26,240 --> 00:10:27,400
through the storms of the future.

169
00:10:36,560 --> 00:10:37,160
Yongnian,

170
00:10:38,360 --> 00:10:39,920
would you stop forming sheets already?

171
00:10:43,240 --> 00:10:44,720
A day without forming sheets

172
00:10:45,320 --> 00:10:47,160
is like a day without eating for me.

173
00:10:47,920 --> 00:10:50,160
You've really got it bad, you know.

174
00:10:50,720 --> 00:10:51,640
Then tell me,

175
00:10:52,400 --> 00:10:53,400
in your heart,

176
00:10:54,280 --> 00:10:55,360
what kind of paper

177
00:10:55,480 --> 00:10:57,160
counts as truly great paper?

178
00:10:59,240 --> 00:11:00,640
If you can explain it clearly,

179
00:11:01,040 --> 00:11:01,920
I'll make paper with you.

180
00:11:03,040 --> 00:11:05,040
But if you can't give me a proper answer,

181
00:11:06,360 --> 00:11:07,280
I won't join you.

182
00:11:14,240 --> 00:11:15,400
You'll listen to Xiu Mei.

183
00:11:16,400 --> 00:11:17,280
The two of you go out for a stroll.

184
00:11:17,280 --> 00:11:18,400
I'll watch the house for you.

185
00:11:34,440 --> 00:11:35,920
I'm not interested.

186
00:11:36,680 --> 00:11:37,640
I knew it.

187
00:11:38,360 --> 00:11:39,640
No matter how much I say,

188
00:11:40,280 --> 00:11:41,480
you won't listen anyway.

189
00:11:43,360 --> 00:11:45,120
Let me help you form a few sheets.

190
00:11:48,480 --> 00:11:49,520
Old Man.

191
00:11:50,040 --> 00:11:52,400
Hell has truly frozen over.

192
00:11:52,600 --> 00:11:53,640
What brings you here?

193
00:11:53,760 --> 00:11:55,280
Back at Hongxing Factory,

194
00:11:55,280 --> 00:11:56,760
I was your Sheet Lifter.

195
00:11:56,920 --> 00:11:58,920
We haven't worked together in years.

196
00:11:59,480 --> 00:12:01,000
Don't you want to see my craft again?

197
00:12:02,120 --> 00:12:03,440
Are you kidding me?

198
00:12:03,560 --> 00:12:05,160
You're a venerable master now.

199
00:12:05,360 --> 00:12:06,680
Having you as my Sheet Lifter,

200
00:12:06,760 --> 00:12:07,560
that wouldn't be right.

201
00:12:07,560 --> 00:12:09,280
I want to be your Sheet Lifter.

202
00:12:09,520 --> 00:12:11,120
What, not allowed?

203
00:12:12,360 --> 00:12:13,360
Well, if you put it that way,

204
00:12:14,240 --> 00:12:15,640
then I won't stand on ceremony.

205
00:12:16,600 --> 00:12:17,000
Come on.

206
00:12:17,320 --> 00:12:17,800
Here we go.

207
00:12:25,160 --> 00:12:25,560
Lift!

208
00:12:45,000 --> 00:12:45,560
Here we go!

209
00:12:53,240 --> 00:12:55,280
Two national-level Intangible Cultural Heritage Inheritors

210
00:12:56,040 --> 00:12:57,280
forming a single sheet together

211
00:12:57,640 --> 00:12:58,840
A rare sight indeed!

212
00:13:01,800 --> 00:13:04,480
The greatest sound is silence; the greatest form is formless

213
00:13:04,920 --> 00:13:06,160
True masters, no doubt.

214
00:13:06,760 --> 00:13:08,360
You haven't lost your touch!

215
00:13:08,680 --> 00:13:09,880
Just so-so, I guess.

216
00:13:34,040 --> 00:13:36,440
You only come when you need something.

217
00:13:37,040 --> 00:13:38,880
I guess today is no exception.

218
00:13:41,200 --> 00:13:42,120
Actually...

219
00:13:43,160 --> 00:13:45,360
At the Four Treasures of the Study Festival,

220
00:13:45,520 --> 00:13:46,440
Guan Shan came to see you

221
00:13:46,880 --> 00:13:48,280
because he wanted to discuss something.

222
00:13:49,040 --> 00:13:50,280
During the meal,

223
00:13:51,040 --> 00:13:52,520
I could see you weren't in a great mood,

224
00:13:52,920 --> 00:13:54,400
so I didn't bring it up again.

225
00:13:57,040 --> 00:13:58,840
Guan Shan has a long-cherished wish.

226
00:13:59,600 --> 00:14:01,000
He wants to make a sheet

227
00:14:01,400 --> 00:14:04,440
that represents peak Xuan paper craft.

228
00:14:06,360 --> 00:14:07,920
This idea of his

229
00:14:08,280 --> 00:14:11,440
is shared by Beijing Museum and experts.

230
00:14:13,360 --> 00:14:17,200
That's exactly why Guan Shan sent me here.

231
00:14:22,840 --> 00:14:25,520
Chairman Guan really thinks highly of me.

232
00:14:28,040 --> 00:14:30,600
But with you here, Old Man,

233
00:14:31,360 --> 00:14:33,000
what paper couldn't be made?

234
00:14:34,400 --> 00:14:36,040
I just told you,

235
00:14:36,240 --> 00:14:39,200
it must represent peak Xuan paper craft.

236
00:14:39,800 --> 00:14:42,520
Honestly, on my own,

237
00:14:43,680 --> 00:14:45,240
I have no confidence at all.

238
00:14:46,240 --> 00:14:47,280
Is it really that difficult?

239
00:14:48,440 --> 00:14:50,160
It's not a question of difficulty.

240
00:14:51,160 --> 00:14:52,040
It's the size.

241
00:14:52,760 --> 00:14:53,400
How big?

242
00:14:53,760 --> 00:14:55,040
A single sheet of Xuan paper,

243
00:14:55,920 --> 00:14:57,000
Sanzhangsan (11-meter).

244
00:14:59,440 --> 00:15:00,640
Sanzhangsan (11-meter)?

245
00:15:06,760 --> 00:15:09,440
Chairman Guan must be joking, right?

246
00:15:11,280 --> 00:15:12,760
He's not joking at all.

247
00:15:13,360 --> 00:15:14,920
The Sanzhangsan (11-meter) project

248
00:15:14,920 --> 00:15:17,240
leadership task force has been formed.

249
00:15:24,240 --> 00:15:25,040
Old Man,

250
00:15:26,160 --> 00:15:27,760
let's set aside for now

251
00:15:29,280 --> 00:15:32,280
if such a huge sheet can even be made.

252
00:15:32,720 --> 00:15:34,240
For over a thousand years,

253
00:15:34,640 --> 00:15:37,280
the largest Xuan paper our ancestors made

254
00:15:37,280 --> 00:15:38,560
was only two-zhang.

255
00:15:38,880 --> 00:15:39,040
Right.

256
00:15:39,040 --> 00:15:39,520
Isn't that so?

257
00:15:40,000 --> 00:15:42,920
Painters who work on two-zhang paper

258
00:15:43,640 --> 00:15:45,360
are already few and far between.

259
00:15:46,520 --> 00:15:49,440
Make Sanzhangsan (11-meter) paper now?

260
00:15:50,880 --> 00:15:52,520
What would anyone use it for?

261
00:15:55,000 --> 00:15:56,000
Lao Xuan,

262
00:15:58,040 --> 00:16:01,360
masters Fu Baoshi and Guan Shanyue

263
00:16:01,840 --> 00:16:04,640
jointly created a piece for the Great Hall of the People,

264
00:16:04,640 --> 00:16:06,680
The Land So Rich in Beauty.

265
00:16:07,120 --> 00:16:09,400
What a magnificent masterpiece it was!

266
00:16:09,520 --> 00:16:11,520
But limited by sheet-forming technology,

267
00:16:13,520 --> 00:16:16,440
they had to join 13 four-meter sheets.

268
00:16:17,280 --> 00:16:19,480
You have to admit, that's a real shame.

269
00:16:20,680 --> 00:16:22,400
Guan Shan said at the meeting,

270
00:16:23,600 --> 00:16:27,440
it's the best era for Xuan paper artisans.

271
00:16:28,440 --> 00:16:30,920
We can now make Sanzhangsan (11-meter).

272
00:16:31,520 --> 00:16:34,120
We need a Sanzhangsan (11-meter) sheet,

273
00:16:35,040 --> 00:16:37,520
to stand at the peak of Xuan paper craft,

274
00:16:37,920 --> 00:16:40,880
raise the Sanzhangsan (11-meter) banner.

275
00:16:42,680 --> 00:16:45,760
It's not a question of whether it will be used.

276
00:16:53,040 --> 00:16:53,840
Old Man,

277
00:16:59,440 --> 00:17:01,200
this is really asking too much of me.

278
00:17:02,520 --> 00:17:03,360
Lao Xuan,

279
00:17:04,119 --> 00:17:05,040
if it weren't a challenge,

280
00:17:05,880 --> 00:17:07,640
why would I come to you?

281
00:17:08,240 --> 00:17:09,880
Sanzhangsan (11-meter) is a good thing,

282
00:17:10,240 --> 00:17:12,599
but I won't partner with Hongxing Factory.

283
00:17:13,119 --> 00:17:14,359
I'll do it on my own.

284
00:17:34,880 --> 00:17:35,640
Master Xuan

285
00:17:37,400 --> 00:17:38,000
Busy at work?

286
00:18:00,760 --> 00:18:01,400
Master.

287
00:18:02,160 --> 00:18:03,880
Why didn't you let me know you were coming?

288
00:18:03,880 --> 00:18:06,000
Just give me a call if you need anything.

289
00:18:06,120 --> 00:18:06,920
I'll take care of it.

290
00:18:07,160 --> 00:18:08,600
How big is this workshop of yours?

291
00:18:10,520 --> 00:18:12,000
Measuring from the highest point,

292
00:18:12,000 --> 00:18:13,160
it's just under seven meters.

293
00:18:16,440 --> 00:18:17,360
Is there something you need?

294
00:18:18,520 --> 00:18:20,160
I need to find a big workshop.

295
00:18:20,480 --> 00:18:21,840
How big does it need to be?

296
00:18:22,960 --> 00:18:24,920
No less than 25 meters long,

297
00:18:25,200 --> 00:18:26,640
no less than 10 meters wide,

298
00:18:26,840 --> 00:18:28,480
and no less than eight meters high.

299
00:18:28,760 --> 00:18:31,600
And the workshop must be empty inside.

300
00:18:31,840 --> 00:18:33,120
An empty factory won't be easy to find.

301
00:18:33,680 --> 00:18:34,760
This workshop of mine

302
00:18:34,960 --> 00:18:36,480
is the biggest in Peach Blossom Town.

303
00:18:39,160 --> 00:18:41,800
What do you need an empty factory for?

304
00:18:43,960 --> 00:18:45,080
Okay, I got it.

305
00:18:47,400 --> 00:18:48,120
Master.

306
00:18:48,760 --> 00:18:49,480
Master.

307
00:18:58,840 --> 00:19:00,240
You're still in the mood for a morning jog?

308
00:19:00,720 --> 00:19:01,840
I can only run for half an hour.

309
00:19:01,840 --> 00:19:02,360
I've got a meeting soon.

310
00:19:02,360 --> 00:19:02,920
Stop running, stop running.

311
00:19:03,120 --> 00:19:03,760
Come on, tell me.

312
00:19:05,160 --> 00:19:05,600
Tell you what?

313
00:19:05,600 --> 00:19:06,520
Come on, tell me.

314
00:19:06,520 --> 00:19:07,720
About Master's Sanzhangsan (11-meter),

315
00:19:08,360 --> 00:19:10,000
how does he plan to pull it off?

316
00:19:11,000 --> 00:19:12,240
It's tough. He hasn't figured it out yet.

317
00:19:13,040 --> 00:19:13,560
No matter how tough it is,

318
00:19:13,560 --> 00:19:15,520
as his disciple, I've got to help him.

319
00:19:16,240 --> 00:19:17,760
First see if he even acknowledges you.

320
00:19:18,080 --> 00:19:19,760
Look at the situation. Don't say that.

321
00:19:20,720 --> 00:19:21,720
Go back and tell Master,

322
00:19:23,080 --> 00:19:24,760
he needs a big workshop, I'll build it.

323
00:19:25,200 --> 00:19:26,240
Not enough people, I'll get them.

324
00:19:26,400 --> 00:19:28,040
Money's not something he needs to worry about.

325
00:19:28,040 --> 00:19:30,000
If I, his Head Disciple, don't help him,

326
00:19:30,240 --> 00:19:31,960
he'll really struggle to do it alone.

327
00:19:32,720 --> 00:19:34,640
You think with your help it'll work out?

328
00:19:36,800 --> 00:19:38,840
Well, two heads are better than one.

329
00:19:39,080 --> 00:19:41,840
I'm at least smarter than average, right?

330
00:19:47,000 --> 00:19:47,880
Don't think

331
00:19:48,680 --> 00:19:50,960
that by calling yourself Head Disciple,

332
00:19:51,760 --> 00:19:52,640
you can actually handle this.

333
00:19:53,400 --> 00:19:54,560
Let me ask you a few questions.

334
00:19:55,200 --> 00:19:56,920
If you can answer even one,

335
00:19:57,280 --> 00:19:57,920
I'll help you.

336
00:19:58,400 --> 00:19:58,920
Go ahead.

337
00:19:59,480 --> 00:20:01,080
Your Master's been developing

338
00:20:01,240 --> 00:20:04,000
a mould frame 11.4 by 3.7 meters.

339
00:20:04,200 --> 00:20:06,240
Sheet Masters and Lifters need 44 people,

340
00:20:06,520 --> 00:20:08,200
plus 12 to lift the screen.

341
00:20:08,520 --> 00:20:10,280
Solid sheet-forming skills

342
00:20:10,280 --> 00:20:11,640
are the bare minimum.

343
00:20:12,080 --> 00:20:15,080
Height, build, and strength must match.

344
00:20:16,000 --> 00:20:16,720
You tell me,

345
00:20:17,040 --> 00:20:18,080
where are you going to find these people?

346
00:20:19,000 --> 00:20:20,000
That many people?

347
00:20:21,680 --> 00:20:24,720
It's a mould frame over ten meters long.

348
00:20:25,480 --> 00:20:26,520
Once it's soaked with water,

349
00:20:26,560 --> 00:20:28,440
it'll weigh well over a thousand pounds.

350
00:20:28,440 --> 00:20:29,320
What kind of material

351
00:20:29,320 --> 00:20:31,040
can you guarantee is both liftable

352
00:20:31,480 --> 00:20:32,920
and won't warp after absorbing water?

353
00:20:36,400 --> 00:20:38,440
Normally, after sheet forming,

354
00:20:38,960 --> 00:20:39,960
lifting up the sheet-forming screen

355
00:20:40,600 --> 00:20:41,880
and placing it on the paper stack is easy.

356
00:20:42,400 --> 00:20:44,000
But this sheet-forming screen is

357
00:20:44,360 --> 00:20:45,920
11 meters long and 3.7 meters wide.

358
00:20:46,680 --> 00:20:47,760
Come on, you tell me,

359
00:20:48,520 --> 00:20:51,320
how can you ensure after lifting it,

360
00:20:51,720 --> 00:20:53,520
it lands perfectly on the paper stack?

361
00:21:01,560 --> 00:21:02,400
All right, I get it.

362
00:21:02,600 --> 00:21:04,280
I'll hurry back and think of something.

363
00:21:04,760 --> 00:21:05,200
Brother,

364
00:21:05,920 --> 00:21:07,240
this is a great opportunity.

365
00:21:07,680 --> 00:21:09,000
You've got to help me out.

366
00:21:09,080 --> 00:21:10,000
If we pull this off,

367
00:21:11,000 --> 00:21:12,760
the rift between me and Master will be mended.

368
00:21:13,760 --> 00:21:14,240
Let's just

369
00:21:14,240 --> 00:21:16,000
wait and see how the old man handles it.

370
00:21:16,320 --> 00:21:18,000
He's been out looking around for days,

371
00:21:18,520 --> 00:21:19,840
with nothing to show for it.

372
00:21:20,200 --> 00:21:20,840
Okay, I got it.

373
00:21:21,240 --> 00:21:21,960
Lao Ren.

374
00:21:23,040 --> 00:21:24,240
What time is it? You're still not up?

375
00:21:24,680 --> 00:21:25,640
I need to talk to you, it's urgent.

376
00:21:26,600 --> 00:21:28,080
That water you brought me, you drank it yourself.

377
00:21:28,160 --> 00:21:29,200
Wait for my word, wait for my word.

378
00:21:29,480 --> 00:21:30,280
Didn't I tell you,

379
00:21:31,240 --> 00:21:33,080
Master's Sanzhangsan (11-meter) project.

380
00:21:33,800 --> 00:21:34,680
You wait for me at home.

381
00:21:48,760 --> 00:21:49,280
Look at him.

382
00:21:50,240 --> 00:21:51,760
Takes off without saying a word.

383
00:21:51,920 --> 00:21:53,240
Comes back without a greeting either.

384
00:21:54,000 --> 00:21:56,000
Someone must have made him angry.

385
00:22:04,040 --> 00:22:05,800
Did you tell Jiang Ziliu

386
00:22:06,280 --> 00:22:07,760
that I'll make Sanzhangsan (11-meter)?

387
00:22:08,760 --> 00:22:10,480
No, I didn't.

388
00:22:10,920 --> 00:22:11,800
I never said a word.

389
00:22:13,080 --> 00:22:14,800
Then how could he possibly know

390
00:22:15,360 --> 00:22:16,400
that I'm making Sanzhangsan (11-meter)?

391
00:22:17,200 --> 00:22:18,720
Well, go ask whoever you need to.

392
00:22:18,720 --> 00:22:19,520
I didn't say anything, that's for sure.

393
00:22:19,920 --> 00:22:21,760
Jiang Ziliu wants Sanzhangsan (11-meter)?

394
00:22:22,080 --> 00:22:22,920
Yeah.

395
00:22:23,120 --> 00:22:23,720
I mean, come on.

396
00:22:24,480 --> 00:22:26,000
He's already so old.

397
00:22:27,000 --> 00:22:27,720
Even if it killed him,

398
00:22:27,720 --> 00:22:29,280
he couldn't paint something that huge.

399
00:22:31,080 --> 00:22:32,120
I bet

400
00:22:33,040 --> 00:22:35,080
he heard Hongxing Factory was after me,

401
00:22:35,800 --> 00:22:37,680
so he's messing with me on purpose.

402
00:22:44,000 --> 00:22:45,440
All right, drop that for now.

403
00:22:46,400 --> 00:22:46,960
Let me ask you something.

404
00:22:47,680 --> 00:22:48,960
Lao Xie's wife said

405
00:22:49,200 --> 00:22:51,160
you went wandering around town today,

406
00:22:51,320 --> 00:22:52,560
looking around all over the place.

407
00:22:53,240 --> 00:22:54,080
What were you actually doing?

408
00:22:58,360 --> 00:22:59,440
I went shopping.

409
00:23:00,960 --> 00:23:01,240
Shopping?

410
00:23:05,320 --> 00:23:07,720
Have you ever seen him go shopping in his life?

411
00:23:08,800 --> 00:23:10,680
Something's clearly on his mind.

412
00:23:11,000 --> 00:23:13,200
I think that leader Guan Shan is a good man.

413
00:23:13,680 --> 00:23:15,480
He's humble toward talent.

414
00:23:16,240 --> 00:23:18,360
He's come to invite you time and time again,

415
00:23:18,360 --> 00:23:20,240
and you've refused him time and again.

416
00:23:20,240 --> 00:23:22,920
He lowered himself to ask you again.

417
00:23:23,200 --> 00:23:24,920
If it were me, I'd have given up on you long ago.

418
00:23:25,480 --> 00:23:26,240
And that Old Man too.

419
00:23:26,920 --> 00:23:27,520
Tell me,

420
00:23:27,760 --> 00:23:30,080
when have you ever shown him any respect?

421
00:23:30,280 --> 00:23:30,960
The other day,

422
00:23:31,200 --> 00:23:33,920
it was mealtime, I'd cooked dinner,

423
00:23:33,920 --> 00:23:35,240
and you didn't even ask him to stay for a bite.

424
00:23:35,680 --> 00:23:37,600
Old Man and I are Senior Brothers.

425
00:23:38,200 --> 00:23:40,000
It doesn't matter whether he eats or not.

426
00:23:40,720 --> 00:23:42,320
That's not a big deal at all.

427
00:23:42,520 --> 00:23:44,160
How is it not a big deal?

428
00:23:44,280 --> 00:23:45,760
He couldn't even eat.

429
00:23:45,920 --> 00:23:48,320
He failed his task and couldn't report.

430
00:23:50,320 --> 00:23:51,400
Well, then, tell me,

431
00:23:52,160 --> 00:23:53,560
how am I supposed to agree to them?

432
00:23:54,680 --> 00:23:55,320
Yongnian.

433
00:23:56,400 --> 00:23:58,080
Tell me, this Sanzhangsan (11-meter),

434
00:23:59,080 --> 00:24:00,480
would it count as a piece of paper

435
00:24:00,680 --> 00:24:02,400
worthy of honoring our ancestors?

436
00:24:02,520 --> 00:24:04,080
Of course it would, Senior Brother.

437
00:24:04,480 --> 00:24:05,160
Just think about it.

438
00:24:05,480 --> 00:24:08,320
No ancestor has ever made paper that large.

439
00:24:08,320 --> 00:24:09,560
If we could make it,

440
00:24:09,800 --> 00:24:12,400
then, then we...

441
00:24:12,680 --> 00:24:13,240
Right?

442
00:24:13,440 --> 00:24:14,480
Of course it would count.

443
00:24:14,920 --> 00:24:15,800
If

444
00:24:17,240 --> 00:24:20,240
we craft Sanzhangsan (11-meter) Xuan paper,

445
00:24:23,240 --> 00:24:24,400
unmatched by anyone before us,

446
00:24:26,520 --> 00:24:27,480
if we succeed,

447
00:24:27,960 --> 00:24:30,600
we'll have honored all our ancestors in this lifetime.

448
00:24:30,800 --> 00:24:32,360
And we'll have done justice to

449
00:24:32,360 --> 00:24:34,080
a lifetime spent making paper.

450
00:24:35,040 --> 00:24:35,960
But this thing

451
00:24:36,840 --> 00:24:39,600
isn't as simple as just talking about it.

452
00:24:39,600 --> 00:24:40,360
What's wrong?

453
00:24:43,560 --> 00:24:44,240
What is it?

454
00:24:45,000 --> 00:24:48,400
11.4 meters by 3.7 meters.

455
00:24:49,840 --> 00:24:54,200
Look, how do you build a mould frame that big?

456
00:24:55,240 --> 00:24:56,840
And the sheet-forming screen,

457
00:24:57,320 --> 00:24:58,960
and the vat for sheet forming...

458
00:24:59,440 --> 00:25:00,480
I thought about it,

459
00:25:01,920 --> 00:25:03,680
and it's practically a swimming pool.

460
00:25:04,200 --> 00:25:06,040
A single two-zhang sheet of Xuan paper

461
00:25:06,720 --> 00:25:08,280
takes over ten people to form.

462
00:25:09,320 --> 00:25:10,800
Let alone Sanzhangsan (11-meter).

463
00:25:11,400 --> 00:25:13,360
How many people would it take to form that sheet?

464
00:25:14,120 --> 00:25:16,800
Peach Blossom Town's private paper mills

465
00:25:16,800 --> 00:25:18,680
combined wouldn't have that many people.

466
00:25:20,600 --> 00:25:24,040
With Hongxing Factory's strong workforce,

467
00:25:24,400 --> 00:25:25,320
that might just about do it.

468
00:25:30,680 --> 00:25:31,800
So you're saying

469
00:25:33,960 --> 00:25:35,560
you can only partner with Hongxing Factory.

470
00:25:36,000 --> 00:25:39,000
I still can't get past this in my heart.

471
00:25:44,320 --> 00:25:46,080
A genius designer like Xuan Yan

472
00:25:46,080 --> 00:25:46,840
is certainly important.

473
00:25:46,840 --> 00:25:49,200
But I'd suggest you put more effort

474
00:25:49,200 --> 00:25:50,520
into your marketing approach.

475
00:25:50,800 --> 00:25:51,920
Cultivate and build

476
00:25:51,920 --> 00:25:54,440
an online Xuan paper creative community.

477
00:25:55,160 --> 00:25:56,320
What I really mean is,

478
00:25:56,320 --> 00:25:59,040
in traditional craft, it's China's finest.

479
00:26:01,760 --> 00:26:02,680
I understand, Senior Sister.

480
00:26:03,320 --> 00:26:04,800
I'll do my best to persuade my dad.

481
00:26:06,120 --> 00:26:07,320
Don't feel too bad, okay?

482
00:26:08,240 --> 00:26:09,120
Just wait for my news.

483
00:26:10,320 --> 00:26:11,120
Alright, that's it then.

484
00:26:15,720 --> 00:26:16,440
What's wrong?

485
00:26:19,440 --> 00:26:20,520
My master is sick.

486
00:26:29,320 --> 00:26:30,840
My master has pancreatic cancer.

487
00:26:30,840 --> 00:26:32,400
It was already late-stage when diagnosed.

488
00:26:33,080 --> 00:26:35,440
The doctor said without surgery,

489
00:26:35,440 --> 00:26:37,040
he only has two or three months left.

490
00:26:37,360 --> 00:26:39,520
Even with surgery, it won't buy much time.

491
00:26:40,400 --> 00:26:41,960
And the surgery itself is quite risky.

492
00:26:42,200 --> 00:26:44,560
But upon hearing of Sanzhangsan (11-meter),

493
00:26:44,720 --> 00:26:45,720
he was so thrilled.

494
00:26:46,320 --> 00:26:47,440
He told the doctor,

495
00:26:48,800 --> 00:26:50,760
"I have to gamble on this. It's worth it."

496
00:26:51,320 --> 00:26:53,520
Even for just one more month of life,

497
00:26:54,160 --> 00:26:57,440
he wants, in this final stage of life,

498
00:26:57,720 --> 00:27:00,040
to paint one last great masterpiece.

499
00:27:04,560 --> 00:27:05,120
By the way, Dad,

500
00:27:05,720 --> 00:27:07,240
when my master called you,

501
00:27:07,760 --> 00:27:09,040
he was about to enter the operating room.

502
00:27:09,560 --> 00:27:10,680
He called me too.

503
00:27:10,920 --> 00:27:11,760
I did answer,

504
00:27:12,200 --> 00:27:14,280
but he never told me he was hospitalized.

505
00:27:15,240 --> 00:27:17,200
Uncle Xuan, this isn't your fault.

506
00:27:19,760 --> 00:27:20,560
You tell me first,

507
00:27:20,920 --> 00:27:22,160
how is he doing now?

508
00:27:22,520 --> 00:27:23,480
My Senior Sister told me

509
00:27:23,480 --> 00:27:25,320
he's out of surgery but hasn't woken up.

510
00:27:25,320 --> 00:27:26,720
But the surgery should be a success.

511
00:27:27,920 --> 00:27:28,920
Oh, and he also said

512
00:27:29,440 --> 00:27:31,920
he wants to see my dad.

513
00:27:33,480 --> 00:27:34,200
Alright then.

514
00:27:35,520 --> 00:27:36,720
Is there still time if I leave now?

515
00:28:13,480 --> 00:28:13,880
Dad.

516
00:28:14,800 --> 00:28:15,160
Dad.

517
00:28:17,680 --> 00:28:18,760
I bought some food.

518
00:28:19,280 --> 00:28:20,040
Have a bite.

519
00:28:25,560 --> 00:28:26,720
I don't want to eat.

520
00:28:36,080 --> 00:28:36,920
You're awake.

521
00:28:44,560 --> 00:28:45,520
Master Jiang.

522
00:28:47,920 --> 00:28:48,760
You're awake.

523
00:28:50,720 --> 00:28:51,520
Good, you're awake.

524
00:28:52,520 --> 00:28:54,200
Xuan Yongnian, Xuan Yongnian.

525
00:28:56,680 --> 00:28:58,760
Did our talking wake you up?

526
00:28:58,800 --> 00:28:59,240
Did it?

527
00:29:02,040 --> 00:29:03,240
You came.

528
00:29:04,400 --> 00:29:04,960
Yes, I came.

529
00:29:05,720 --> 00:29:08,200
Did you drink the Douzhi?

530
00:29:14,680 --> 00:29:16,960
You've been pushing that stuff on me for years.

531
00:29:16,960 --> 00:29:17,800
I won't drink it.

532
00:29:18,360 --> 00:29:20,680
That stuff tastes like stinky socks.

533
00:29:21,400 --> 00:29:22,240
I won't drink it.

534
00:29:23,920 --> 00:29:24,720
You...

535
00:29:26,080 --> 00:29:27,840
You don't have a clue.

536
00:29:30,040 --> 00:29:30,720
You just don't get it.

537
00:29:32,440 --> 00:29:33,200
Oh, you get it, huh?

538
00:29:35,520 --> 00:29:37,480
You "got it" all the way into this hospital bed.

539
00:29:42,240 --> 00:29:43,000
Master.

540
00:29:44,160 --> 00:29:46,400
You've cheated death this time.

541
00:29:46,520 --> 00:29:46,920
Dad.

542
00:29:47,520 --> 00:29:48,440
Sit down and chat.

543
00:29:50,520 --> 00:29:51,880
Won't be long now.

544
00:29:55,600 --> 00:29:57,840
Can we not talk like that?

545
00:30:01,000 --> 00:30:03,480
Good people don't live long.

546
00:30:03,720 --> 00:30:05,560
Bad people live a thousand years.

547
00:30:08,520 --> 00:30:10,240
You old rascal.

548
00:30:11,160 --> 00:30:13,600
Still holding in a curse for me.

549
00:30:14,880 --> 00:30:15,520
You...

550
00:30:16,520 --> 00:30:16,960
Master.

551
00:30:17,920 --> 00:30:18,760
Master. Dad.

552
00:30:19,200 --> 00:30:19,960
Master.

553
00:30:19,960 --> 00:30:20,720
Go get the nurse.

554
00:30:20,840 --> 00:30:21,520
I'll go.

555
00:30:21,520 --> 00:30:22,320
Hurry, hurry.

556
00:30:24,760 --> 00:30:26,440
Easy, easy, easy.

557
00:30:34,760 --> 00:30:36,000
Easy, Master Jiang.

558
00:30:36,000 --> 00:30:37,240
Master Jiang, take it easy.

559
00:30:41,080 --> 00:30:41,720
Master Jiang.

560
00:30:44,000 --> 00:30:46,840
I heard you still want to paint.

561
00:30:47,520 --> 00:30:48,760
In your condition?

562
00:30:50,160 --> 00:30:51,520
Just rest up properly.

563
00:30:52,200 --> 00:30:54,040
Stop thinking about painting.

564
00:30:54,960 --> 00:30:56,600
Then what should I do?

565
00:30:58,240 --> 00:31:02,800
Just sit around waiting to die like you?

566
00:31:05,240 --> 00:31:10,120
I'm old but still ambitious.

567
00:31:13,000 --> 00:31:16,440
In this state, what ambition?

568
00:31:20,800 --> 00:31:21,680
Lao Xuan.

569
00:31:25,200 --> 00:31:27,280
If you can make me

570
00:31:27,280 --> 00:31:30,480
this Sanzhangsan (11-meter) Xuan paper,

571
00:31:32,440 --> 00:31:33,600
I guarantee

572
00:31:34,040 --> 00:31:37,160
I'll jump right off this bed and paint.

573
00:31:38,520 --> 00:31:39,480
And what's more,

574
00:31:43,680 --> 00:31:48,320
I'll paint better than ever before.

575
00:31:50,040 --> 00:31:54,240
Master Jiang, you sure know how to joke.

576
00:31:54,240 --> 00:31:56,920
Cracking jokes at a time like this.

577
00:31:57,680 --> 00:31:59,680
Just admit you can't make it.

578
00:32:00,800 --> 00:32:01,400
And forget it.

579
00:32:04,720 --> 00:32:06,360
If you can really paint again,

580
00:32:07,960 --> 00:32:10,440
I, Xuan Yongnian, will surely make it.

581
00:32:10,520 --> 00:32:12,520
The Sanzhangsan (11-meter) you want.

582
00:32:12,760 --> 00:32:14,320
If you can make it,

583
00:32:14,520 --> 00:32:16,000
I'll definitely paint.

584
00:32:16,800 --> 00:32:17,960
If you can paint,

585
00:32:19,640 --> 00:32:21,520
I'll definitely make it.

586
00:32:22,760 --> 00:32:23,240
Lao Xuan.

587
00:32:26,520 --> 00:32:30,480
I have no time to joke around with you.

588
00:32:34,520 --> 00:32:37,520
Master Jiang, I don't have time to joke either.

589
00:32:42,080 --> 00:32:44,080
I'm afraid you won't wait for me.

590
00:32:48,640 --> 00:32:52,840
Set your mind at ease.

591
00:32:54,760 --> 00:32:57,040
Just for this paper of yours,

592
00:32:58,840 --> 00:33:00,680
I won't die.

593
00:33:09,240 --> 00:33:11,880
A gentleman's word

594
00:33:14,240 --> 00:33:15,760
is his bond.

595
00:33:50,920 --> 00:33:51,320
Dad.

596
00:33:53,320 --> 00:33:54,040
Uncle Xuan.

597
00:34:00,960 --> 00:34:01,680
Uncle Xuan.

598
00:34:03,040 --> 00:34:06,000
My dad asked me to give this to you.

599
00:34:19,920 --> 00:34:20,719
Your father...

600
00:34:24,560 --> 00:34:26,440
is a truly remarkable man.

601
00:34:32,040 --> 00:34:33,000
Take good care of him.

602
00:34:38,760 --> 00:34:39,719
Take good care of Master.

603
00:35:08,080 --> 00:35:13,000
Your 1994 Semi-Sized Ribbed Xuan Paper.

604
00:35:14,000 --> 00:35:16,440
I tested it out in midsummer of 1998.

605
00:35:17,400 --> 00:35:18,080
The strengths:

606
00:35:18,520 --> 00:35:20,200
This paper is lively and spirited.

607
00:35:20,240 --> 00:35:23,280
It gives clouds that soft, fuzzy quality.

608
00:35:23,560 --> 00:35:24,720
Vivid and captivating.

609
00:35:25,000 --> 00:35:28,480
As if you could hear water flowing on it.

610
00:35:29,040 --> 00:35:30,200
The weaknesses are just as clear.

611
00:35:30,800 --> 00:35:33,200
The paper's density is lacking.

612
00:35:33,880 --> 00:35:37,880
For Wang Ximeng's Layered ink wash,

613
00:35:38,520 --> 00:35:39,840
it likely couldn't hold up.

614
00:35:44,080 --> 00:35:45,840
You haven't slept all night, have you?

615
00:35:55,160 --> 00:35:56,160
Take a look.

616
00:35:58,960 --> 00:36:00,040
It's from Master Jiang.

617
00:36:22,640 --> 00:36:24,360
Every single stack, every bundle

618
00:36:25,520 --> 00:36:27,680
All these years he's bought our paper

619
00:36:28,280 --> 00:36:30,280
He left a review on every single stack

620
00:36:34,640 --> 00:36:36,120
This Master Jiang

621
00:36:38,000 --> 00:36:39,440
truly moved me

622
00:36:40,800 --> 00:36:42,960
Every time he offered criticism

623
00:36:45,040 --> 00:36:49,040
I always thought he was just nitpicking

624
00:36:51,000 --> 00:36:52,520
I never imagined

625
00:36:54,000 --> 00:36:57,840
Master Jiang put in so much heart

626
00:37:00,120 --> 00:37:02,960
To meet such a master in my lifetime

627
00:37:05,680 --> 00:37:07,680
I count myself blessed

628
00:37:16,920 --> 00:37:18,560
What about Sanzhangsan (11-meter)?

629
00:37:20,320 --> 00:37:22,080
Let me stay here a little longer

630
00:37:24,400 --> 00:37:25,720
I'll go make you breakfast

631
00:37:29,280 --> 00:37:30,600
Tell me, what kind of paper

632
00:37:31,400 --> 00:37:32,960
counts as truly great paper?

633
00:37:33,240 --> 00:37:36,640
Dense as midnight dew,

634
00:37:37,520 --> 00:37:39,840
light as mist behind a veil...

635
00:37:40,720 --> 00:37:43,600
Saturated, it bears mountains' weight

636
00:37:44,280 --> 00:37:47,200
Spread, it reveals five colors' mystery

637
00:37:48,000 --> 00:37:51,280
Dry, it shows metal and stone's strength

638
00:37:52,120 --> 00:37:55,640
Wet, it captures Jiangnan's misty charm.

639
00:37:56,680 --> 00:37:59,040
Ink seeps into texture, ripples spreading

640
00:37:59,040 --> 00:38:01,720
Like haloed moon on river, star in pool.

641
00:38:01,800 --> 00:38:06,400
This stroke conceals all of yin and yang.

642
00:38:08,840 --> 00:38:10,400
Year 2001

643
00:38:11,360 --> 00:38:14,040
Xuan Yongnian's premium Xuan paper

644
00:38:14,040 --> 00:38:16,640
Tested in late autumn, 2003

645
00:38:16,720 --> 00:38:18,480
Strengths of this paper:

646
00:38:19,760 --> 00:38:22,320
Moist and smooth

647
00:38:22,800 --> 00:38:26,160
Wingceltis bark fibers interwoven evenly

648
00:38:26,600 --> 00:38:30,040
Water absorption rate is just right

649
00:38:31,120 --> 00:38:31,960
Excellent

650
00:38:55,520 --> 00:38:56,680
Sanzhangsan (11-meter)

651
00:39:45,160 --> 00:39:46,520
He's been painting for three days now

652
00:39:47,480 --> 00:39:49,000
And it looks the same as day one

653
00:39:57,160 --> 00:39:59,960
I'm just worried you'll worry yourself sick

654
00:40:35,720 --> 00:40:36,360
Yongnian

655
00:40:37,960 --> 00:40:38,760
Have some water.

656
00:40:43,080 --> 00:40:45,520
Let's have a chat, us old buddies.

657
00:40:47,520 --> 00:40:48,080
Alright.

658
00:40:50,520 --> 00:40:51,120
Look,

659
00:40:51,960 --> 00:40:55,560
you've been shut in here scribbling away

660
00:40:55,560 --> 00:40:56,520
for days now.

661
00:40:56,840 --> 00:40:59,440
We both know deep down,

662
00:41:01,280 --> 00:41:03,360
we can't gather enough people.

663
00:41:03,680 --> 00:41:05,640
And we don't understand the machinery.

664
00:41:06,720 --> 00:41:08,000
I hate to say it,

665
00:41:08,120 --> 00:41:11,640
but on our own, we can't pull this off.

666
00:41:20,360 --> 00:41:22,200
So what do we do if we can't?

667
00:41:23,720 --> 00:41:25,720
Master Jiang Ziliu is in the hospital.

668
00:41:28,840 --> 00:41:32,360
He's holding on for Sanzhangsan (11-meter).

669
00:41:32,920 --> 00:41:35,000
My whole life, I, Xuan Yongnian,

670
00:41:35,040 --> 00:41:37,000
have done nothing but Xuan paper.

671
00:41:39,360 --> 00:41:42,200
If I can't make Sanzhangsan (11-meter),

672
00:41:45,880 --> 00:41:48,680
Master Jiang will carry that regret to his grave.

673
00:41:53,240 --> 00:41:55,080
I'm not telling you to quit.

674
00:41:56,960 --> 00:41:59,240
I just want you to face reality.

675
00:42:00,360 --> 00:42:02,440
Actually, I figured it out long ago.

676
00:42:02,840 --> 00:42:05,280
Even with all Peach Blossom Town's help,

677
00:42:05,720 --> 00:42:06,920
we still can't do it.

678
00:42:09,840 --> 00:42:11,080
What are you getting at?

679
00:42:12,800 --> 00:42:14,520
If you want to pull this off,

680
00:42:15,000 --> 00:42:16,840
you'll have to go to Hongxing Factory.

681
00:42:23,160 --> 00:42:24,560
I'm just saying.

682
00:42:25,400 --> 00:42:26,360
It's up to you whether to listen.

683
00:42:27,040 --> 00:42:29,000
If anyone else said this, fine.

684
00:42:29,120 --> 00:42:31,160
But how can you say something like that?

685
00:42:32,120 --> 00:42:33,960
To the head of Hongxing Factory back then,

686
00:42:34,080 --> 00:42:36,040
right to his face, what did I say?

687
00:42:36,880 --> 00:42:38,360
I said, in my lifetime, I, Xuan Yongnian,

688
00:42:38,360 --> 00:42:39,520
no matter how at the end of my rope,

689
00:42:39,640 --> 00:42:41,640
I'd never set foot in Hongxing Factory.

690
00:42:42,040 --> 00:42:44,120
That factory head's been replaced several times.

691
00:42:44,200 --> 00:42:45,400
Who cares anymore?

692
00:42:50,400 --> 00:42:52,640
Anyway, I've said my piece, good and bad.

693
00:42:53,720 --> 00:42:54,920
Think it over yourself.
